      "created_at": "2018-09-19T13:00:37.444Z",
      "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Pjer\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"4365\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/ecb155/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Pjer:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>mjafton qe fluturimet nga keto vende ti kryeje per fund-jave, si te premten, te shtunen e te djelen.<br>\nsi fillim i vendos, 1 here ne jave, pastaj duke pare e duke bere.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I nderuar Pjer, po gjate javes cfare te bejne personeli (nga pilotet deri tek mekaniket)? Apo te punojne gjate javes te Gabi dhe ne fundjave fluturime?</p>",
