      "username": "Pjer",
      "name": "Pjer Thomas",
      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/ecb155/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2018-09-20T20:06:30.215Z",
      "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Kthupi\" data-post=\"15\" data-topic=\"4365\" data-full=\"true\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/k/3bc359/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Kthupi:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Swissair nuk operon me ne Shqiperi me sa di une.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>po pritsha pergjigjen tate, per te pare se sa ne brendesi te çeshtjes ishe, dhe e pashe qe ishe jashte orbite.<br>\nnje fare pergjigje ta dha  neuer , dhe per te mesuar se pse swisair falimentoi, meso se pse  sabenaair belge falimentoi, firme qe falimentoi para swisair-it</p>",
      "reply_to_post_number": 15,
      "like_count": 0
